                                        ወታወርደኒ፡ ካእበ፤
                                        <del rend="overUnderlined">ሐ</del><add place="above">ኀ</add>በ፡ ዘቀዳሚ፡ መርገም፤
                                </incipit>
                                <note/>
                            </msItem>
                            
                            
